A blue cube (index 1) sits on top of the rectangle.  A curved block (index 10) sits on top of the rectangle, adjacent to the cube,  This structure has 3 layers.


   **Structure 2 (Pyramid):**  Consists of 4 blocks.  A triangular block (index 13) forms the base.  An orange triangular block (index 14) sits on top of the base triangle. A rectangular block (index 5) is placed horizontally atop the orange triangle. A blue rectangular block (index 5) is placed horizontally atop the green rectangular block and fits inside the structure.  This structure has 3 layers.
